+## Round Finalisation and Snapshot Guarantee
+
+When `gameweek.finaliseRound` is called, it always runs `backfillRoundSnapshots` before `calculateRoundPoints`. This ensures every team that has `TeamPlayer` rows receives a `TeamPlayerSnapshot` for the round, even if their manager made no squad changes during the round.
+
+**Key invariant:** By the time scoring runs, all active teams have a snapshot. Teams that never set up a squad (no `TeamPlayer` rows) score 0 points — this is expected.
+
+```typescript
+// packages/server/src/trpc/routers/gameweek.ts — finaliseRound
+await prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
+  await tx.round.update({ where: { id: roundId }, data: { status: 'complete' } });
+  await backfillRoundSnapshots(tx, tenantId, roundId); // ← guarantees snapshots exist
+  return calculateRoundPoints(tx, tenantId, roundId);
+});
+```
+
+`backfillRoundSnapshots` is idempotent — safe to call multiple times for the same round.
+
